float32.name: Search Distance Lower Bound
float32.tooltip: the smallest distance the code will look for photons. bigger levels need a bigger search radius. Measured, in world units, 0.0 defaults to 1.0

float32.name: Search Distance Upper Bound
float32.tooltip: the largest distance the code will look for photons. bigger levels need a bigger search radius. Measured, in world units, 0.0 defaults to 1.0

float32.name: Luminels Per World Unit
float32.tooltip: how many lightmap pixels there should be per world unit. 0.0 defaults to 3.0

float32.name: Output White Reference
float32.tooltip: what wattage the lightmapper considers "white" to be for output. 0.0 defaults to 1.0

float32.name: Output Black Reference
float32.tooltip: what wattage the lightmapper considers "black" to be for output. 0.0 defaults to 0.0

float32.name: Output Schlick Reference
float32.tooltip: controls the way midtones are mapped. 0.0 defaults to 4.5

float32.name: Diffuse Map Scale
float32.tooltip: controls how diffuse maps are scaled. 0.0 defaults to 1.5
